51
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,200
 It's easier.

52
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:50,900
 Hey, Kazushika Balloon Club!

53
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,600
 Hey, Ryo.

54
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,600
 Are you nervous about the firework festival?

55
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,600
 Yes, I borrowed money.

56
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,600
 Where's the old guy?

57
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,600
 He's in the warehouse.

58
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,600
 If you don't mind, could you lend him to me?

59
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,600
 He has a friend who's interested in it.

60
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,600
 Yes.

61
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,600
 It's a great honor for us to have more friends.

62
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,600
 I don't mind.

63
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:22,300
 Are we going to ride this and go out?

64
00:05:22,300 --> 00:05:26,300
 We can use propane gas for fuel.

65
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:29,300
 Are we going to make ramen in this?

66
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:30,300
 What do you think?

67
