74
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,000
 What?

75
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:58,000
 We'll drive it on the show.

76
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,000
 What?

77
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,000
 You're not asking him to do it?

78
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:07,000
 Do you think he'll be happy to do it?

79
00:06:09,137 --> 00:06:12,700
 Besides, in Japan, it's not allowed to fly at night.

80
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:16,700
 What if the bearded man knows about this plan?

81
00:06:17,624 --> 00:06:19,700
