116
00:08:04,506 --> 00:08:06,436
 I'll try calling it.

117
00:08:13,473 --> 00:08:15,191
 Yes, it's an emergency ramen.

118
00:08:15,216 --> 00:08:16,606
 Are you on your way?

119
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:20,800
 Can I have two ramen, please?

120
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,800
 Yes.

121
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,800
 Two ramen, please.

122
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,164
 Which one do you want?

123
00:08:24,398 --> 00:08:27,584
 No. 8, 3011, Yamada.

124
00:08:27,609 --> 00:08:28,800
 30 times, right?

125
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,800
 Every time.

126
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,800
 I was able to order it properly.

127
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,500
