130
00:08:48,062 --> 00:08:50,062
 It's delicious.

131
00:08:52,955 --> 00:08:54,869
 You're Yamada, right?

132
00:08:54,894 --> 00:08:55,752
 Yes.

133
00:08:55,777 --> 00:08:57,190
 I got it.

134
00:08:57,215 --> 00:08:58,838
 You're fast.

135
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:01,700
 Thank you.

136
00:09:03,098 --> 00:09:04,700
 You're welcome.

137
00:09:07,067 --> 00:09:08,200
 Sorry to keep you waiting.

138
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:10,200
 It's 1,000 yen.

139
