 It's an emergency ramen.

140
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:16,530
 Yes.

141
00:09:16,555 --> 00:09:17,397
 Three ramen.

142
00:09:17,952 --> 00:09:19,163
 Three ramen, please.

143
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,200
 4023, Beat.

144
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,348
 All right.

145
00:09:22,527 --> 00:09:23,551
 It's that room.

146
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,652
 I got it.

147
00:09:28,677 --> 00:09:30,121
 I'm on my way.

148
00:09:35,522 --> 00:09:36,747
 Here's your ramen.

149
00:09:36,772 --> 00:09:38,134
 It's 700 yen.

150
00:09:38,405 --> 00:09:39,622
 Five ramen, please.

151
00:09:39,647 --> 00:09:41,022
 I got it.

152
00:09:41,900 --> 00:09:43,900
 I'm busy.

153
00:09:45,251 --> 00:09:46,437
 Ryo-san.

154
00:09:46,462 --> 00:09:47,411
 Someone called the police.

155
00:09:47,435 --> 00:09:50,232
 Who called the police?

156
00:09:50,325 --> 00:09:51,215
 What should we do?

157
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,082
 It's an emergency.

158
00:09:53,107 --> 00:09:53,900
 Formation.

