00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,900
 It's an emergency.

160
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:57,900
 Where is it?

161
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,900
 It's dark.

162
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,900
 It's too dark to see.

163
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:03,900
 It's a plan to destroy the world.

164
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:07,900
 That's why I painted the ground black.

165
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:09,900
 I'm not good at it.

166
00:10:09,900 --> 00:10:11,900
 If you get caught,

167
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:14,142
 your business will go up.

168
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:18,858
 I didn't think it would go up so much.

169
00:10:18,883 --> 00:10:20,451
 If you do it like this,

170
00:10:20,476 --> 00:10:22,680
 I'll do it on purpose.

171
00:10:22,705 --> 00:10:24,842
 I'm good at it.

172
00:10:24,867 --> 00:10:25,900
 Good.

173
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:29,080
 But is it okay for the police to do part-time jobs?

174
00:10:29,105 --> 00:10:29,900
 Is it okay?

175
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,900
 I'm a police officer.

176
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:33,900
 I have a duty to help people in need.

177
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,900
 If there are people hungry at night,

178
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:37,900
 it's the way to help people.

179
00:10:41,036 --> 00:10:41,900
 A suspicious situation

180
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,900
