182
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:47,900
 It's likely to appear tonight.

183
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:49,900
 It's a big deal.

184
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:51,900
 Enhance the night patrol

185
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,900
