186
00:10:55,900 --> 00:10:57,900
 Do you understand?

187
00:10:57,900 --> 00:11:00,315
 But I don't think it will appear tonight.

188
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:02,596
 Why do you think that?

189
00:11:02,636 --> 00:11:03,915
 That's what I said ?

190
00:11:07,071 --> 00:11:09,071
 I'm a police officer.

191
