 What?

194
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,900
 What do you want to bet?

195
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:18,844
 1,000 yen.

196
00:11:18,869 --> 00:11:20,711
 Idiot!

197
00:11:21,672 --> 00:11:25,305
 Do you think it's okay to do part-time jobs?

198
00:11:25,719 --> 00:11:28,303
 Sir, how about this?

199
00:11:28,328 --> 00:11:29,900
 If Ryo-chan

200
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:31,900
 gets a clue about a suspicious situation,

201
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:35,875
 he can make the fireworks day a holiday.

202
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:37,900
 I see.

203
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,242
 What do you think, Ryo-tsu?

204
00:11:39,267 --> 00:11:40,445
 Is it okay?

205
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:45,900
 That's right.

206
00:11:51,072 --> 00:11:53,072
 Whatever.

207
00:11:53,900 --> 00:11:55,900
 I want to

208
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:57,900
