217
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:15,900
 Can you see a woman?

218
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:17,900
 Well, please take a look.

219
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:19,900
 A bird?

220
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,900
 What?

221
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:23,900
 It's a bird.

222
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:25,900
 It's so dark

223
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:28,421
