229
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:39,900
 That's not good.

230
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:41,900
 Oh, no.

231
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:43,900
 I got something amazing.

232
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:46,541
 Senpai, why don't we find the balloon together

233
00:12:46,566 --> 00:12:47,885
 and get a reward?

234
00:12:48,337 --> 00:12:51,252
 I'll give it to you.

235
00:12:57,900 --> 00:12:59,900
 Hey, what are you doing here?

236
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:01,900
 Oh, Ryo-san.

237
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:03,900
 Well, Ryo-san always

238
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:05,900
 let me make a living,

239
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:07,900
