274
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,383
 Hey, Ryo-san.

275
00:14:26,408 --> 00:14:27,719
 Don't ask me.

276
00:14:27,751 --> 00:14:29,751
 I don't know anything.

277
00:14:30,415 --> 00:14:32,415
 That's right.

278
00:14:41,538 --> 00:14:42,178
 Cat.

